data.description: Experience quintessential country living in this charming farmhouse nestled on 1.5 acres of scenic bliss, flanked by lush trees and farmland. This beloved home, awaiting your personal touch, offers a 30x40 pole barn and a spacious shed for storage. Relax on the expansive covered back deck, overlooking the peaceful backyard retreat. Inside, gather in the large kitchen and dining area for hearty meals, then retreat to the main-floor Master Bedroom with its own bathroom or upstairs to the other two bedrooms. Prepare to be impressed by the expansive 30x40 pole barn, complete with electricity, a durable cement floor, and its own private drive—an ideal space for storing vehicles, equipment, or pursuing hobbies. Additionally, a sizable shed provides ample room for lawn maintenance tools and recreational gear. Come experience the allure of countryside living and dream about turning it into your personal homestead—schedule your tour today!
